  "remarks": "\nAndrei Olgertovich VOLOZHINSKY is a former Vice Admiral and Deputy Chief of the Main Operations Directorate of the General Staff of the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation. \nVOLOZHINSKY has engaged in and provided support for actions or policies which destabilise Ukraine or undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
